What you need to know:

The former Gor Mahia assistant captain joined Simba in August last year on a free transfer after a salary row with K'Ogalo and has cemented his place at the heart of the defence of 21 times Tanzanian League champions.The deal and the amount of money quoted by Manara has however taken Gor Mahia fans by surprise, with most of them venting their anger on social media platforms on why Onyango was allowed to leave for free.